input_str: Wassef Ali Hassoun (Arabic: واصف علي حسون‎; born January 1, 1980) was a United States Marine who was charged with desertion for leaving his unit and engaging with others in a hoax to make it appear that he had been captured by terrorists on June 19, 2004 while serving in Iraq.
